{"tid":373470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港，真係可以靠自己？","createTime":"2017-08-25T04:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T18:35:14.000Z","uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a27dc075363b7d380d4dc3b5e800b5f3684e723f","tid":373470,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T04:51:21.000Z","msg":"話說小弟就不在港，在外國工幹中。<br />\n近日同啲嚟至唔同國家嘅交流生搞咗個文化活動傾傾吓計，我同佢哋講話香港啱啱打完風好亂，講講吓佢哋問到香港係咪一個國家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :外國交流生1<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :外國交流生2<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你哋有自己passoort、貨幣系統、文化、語言，點會唔係一個國家？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你哋有冇軍隊？冇就只可以成為一個受其他國家管轄嘅地區，但你哋有民主可以自己建立軍事嘅嘢再立命自己嘅地區為國家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我哋渴望獨立成為一個國家，但冇軍隊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> +<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :咁你哋等緊啲乜撚嘢？仲唔去馬？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟聽完好撚傷心，我哋所謂嘅民主其實係假民主，我冇同佢哋再解釋。之後佢哋講到民主係要用血汗去爭取而唔係日日坐喺屋企打機，我聽完反而覺得更失望。因為所謂嘅香港人我哋真係日日打機hea下過一日就算數，就算做幾多嘢都係唔夠中共鬥 唉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397e5e8befc058882d0b5f6877eedaa0620c6822","tid":373470,"uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:33:12.000Z","msg":"香港男仔寧願做女神隻兵都唔會為香港當兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532e7abef6cc8c9222fbd308eaf0d0ae67f1d111","tid":373470,"uid":126841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港男仔寧願做女神隻兵都唔會為香港當兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁講法香港真係冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e5ea9b224a999e370b3e8d1d2322020ebf5bac","tid":373470,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T18:35:14.000Z","msg":"證明世事難料呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}